conbody.p:
You execute multiple ALTER TABLE SQL statements in an executable script file. The following
      example shows two statements which are run in a script file. Note the first line in this
      example which must precede the two ALTER TABLE
      statements.#!/opt/hexis/hawkeye-ap/bin/altertbl
alter table tt.table1 add column column1 int64;
alter table tt.table2 add column column2 int64;
